   Our mission is to support the growth and competitiveness of the U.S.
   telecommunications industry by:
     * Promoting international trade and investment opportunities for the
       U.S. telecom industry

     * Providing business counseling to U.S. telecommunications firms
       seeking to enter specific markets

     * Advocating on behalf of U.S. telecommunications firms

     * Conducting market research and statistical analysis of the
       telecommunications industry

